{"tid":1189183,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個話足球係婑人玩？盤點三大高身球王","createTime":"2019-06-06T16:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T12:25:40.000Z","uid":214972,"like":97,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"276b5f71bc99843fac220e35af77716188b9f878","tid":1189183,"uid":214972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:25:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第三位</span><br />\n<br />\nEdin Dzeko 2.03m<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a0wZpxJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa0wZpxJ.png&h=f124e81d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外號波斯尼亞寶石，曾經帶領狼堡勇奪德甲冠軍，本季英超冠軍曼城名宿（轟入五十球，助曼城成為雙料冠軍），現為羅王前鋒重心地位緊貼托迪！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第二位</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3GVCVKD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3GVCVKD.png&h=e69c6d9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRomelu Lukaku 1.90m<br />\n<br />\n人稱渣古，年幼時在青年軍68場轟入150球，憑16歲的年紀成為了歐洲聯賽冠軍盃史上最年輕的球員，現為中游球隊曼聯效力，神童曾力助曼聯旗歐冠十六強賽「巴黎雨夜」3-1奇蹟逆轉聖日耳門！奠定國家隊首席前鋒地位！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第一位</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DAWrQT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DAWrQT.png&h=df742cad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNicklas Bendtner 1.94<br />\n<br />\n曾效力勁旅阿仙奴，祖雲達斯，此子擅攻擅守，其出色搶點防守能力幾乎最代當時阿仙奴主力中堅華美倫位置，為人津津樂道，亦為史上第七名年紀最少登場的丹麥國腳。"},{"pid":"ccb52d1264118714be5dbfd601bac18995ca55e5","tid":1189183,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:33:50.000Z","msg":"針王"},{"pid":"8f4b7876f9ce35ee999944509d97223acbaf48da","tid":1189183,"uid":211049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.